oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of two unidentified men standing by a steam driven grader in front of W. L. Hailey Company. William Leo Hailey (1892-1954) was the founder and president of W.L. Hailey & Company Inc., a water infrastructure company founded in 1925 in Nashville.
